His pension is deposited monthly

52
00:11:16,050 --> 00:11:20,220
有人通过银行转帐把钱取走(西联银行)
and someone is making the occasional
withdrawal. All wire transfers.

53
00:11:21,220 --> 00:11:23,890
没有联邦搜查令 无法查出在哪取钱
l can't find out where
without a federal warrant.

54
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:26,440
他不开车 也不开飞机
Well, he can't drive or fly.

55
00:11:26,640 --> 00:11:27,980
至少不是真名
At least not under his real name.

56
