you decide you've had enough.

867
01:06:35,030 --> 01:06:38,250
看看你为之奋斗的是什么
Time to see
what you've given up your whole life for.

868
01:06:38,450 --> 01:06:40,950
为自己争取一些自由
Maybe get some of that freedom
for yourself.

869
01:06:42,700 --> 01:06:44,120
看看这些人
Look at the people.

870
01:06:45,710 --> 01:06:47,710
现在告诉我哪个是自由的
Now tell me which ones are free.

871
01:06:49,290 --> 01:06:50,970
没债的
Free from debt.

872
01:06:51,380 --> 01:06:52,630
焦虑
Anxiety.

873
01:06:52,710 --> 01:06:53,960
压力
Stress.

874
01:06:54,050 --> 01:06:55,300
恐惧
Fear.

875
01:06:55,380 --> 01:06:59,060
失败 侮辱 背叛
Failure. lndignity. Betrayal.

876
01:07:01,550 --> 01:07:04,560
人们都希望生来就知道现在的事
How many wish they were born
knowing what they know now?

877
01:07:04,640 --> 01:07:06,810
问问自己 有多少人愿意
Ask yourself how many would do things

878
01:07:06,890 --> 01:07:08,570
反覆做同一件事
the same way all over again?

879
01:07:09,650 --> 01:07:12,020
有多少人愿意像我这样生活
And how many would
live their lives like me?

880
01:07:15,400 --> 01:07:18,200
看看对面街上的那辆奥迪车
Now look at the silver Audi
across the street,

881
01:07:18,280 --> 01:07:20,250
整天都在跟踪我
the one that's been following me all day.

882
01:07:20,570 --> 01:07:21,920
那能证明什么
What does that prove?

883
01:07:21,990 --> 01:07:25,420
这是车牌号 多久能查出车主
Here's the tag number.
How long would it take you to run it?

884
01:07:25,500 --> 01:07:28,000
晚上 我不确定 一小时
At this time of night?
l don't know. An hour?

885
01:07:28,080 --> 01:07:29,210
查吧
Do it.

886
01:07:29,920 --> 01:07:32,510
查到后 我就离开
Do it, and then l'll leave.

887
01:07:41,760 --> 01:07:42,930
什么时候
When?

888
01:07:45,930 --> 01:07:50,190
不 这现在是我的问题 我来解决
No, this is my problem now.
l'll handle it.

889
01:07:52,190 --> 01:07:53,310
是的
Yeah?

890
01:07:55,440 --> 01:07:56,530
你暴露了
You're blown.

891
01:07:57,030 --> 01:07:59,280
律师正在查车牌
The lawyer's running the licence plates.

892
01:08:00,610 --> 01:08:02,120
是的
Yeah. So do it?

893
01:08:03,870 --> 01:08:04,910
完成了
Done.

894
01:08:07,620 --> 01:08:09,290
去这个住址
Go to this address.

895
01:08:11,790 --> 01:08:14,420
好吧 假如巴尔没干这事
All right, let's just say
that Barr didn't do it.

896
01:08:14,540 --> 01:08:16,390
或是有人指使他干的
Or did it 'cause someone
put him up to it.

897
01:08:16,460 --> 01:08:17,660
你有什么证据
Either way, what have you got?

898
01:08:17,710 --> 01:08:18,810
是阴谋
Conspiracy.

899
01:08:18,880 --> 01:08:20,680
预谋杀死五个平民百姓 没有动机
Yeah, conspiracy to kill
five random people?

900
01:08:20,760 --> 01:08:22,060
很荒唐 是吗
There's no motive.

901
01:08:22,140 --> 01:08:24,480
荒唐的有点离谱
-lt's ridiculous, right?
-lt's grassy knoll ludicrous.

902
01:08:24,640 --> 01:08:26,390
进一步调查没有意义了
No point looking any further.

903
01:08:26,560 --> 01:08:27,980
没错
Exactly.

904
01:08:28,520 --> 01:08:29,610
说得对
Exactly.

905
01:08:33,150 --> 01:08:34,570
这是什么
What's this?

906
01:08:34,730 --> 01:08:36,830
杀人动机
The motive. Just hold onto it.

907
01:08:36,900 --> 01:08:38,120
我们在玩什么 猜迷游戏
What are we playing, Clue?

908
01:08:39,991 --> 01:08:41,159
Yeah?

909
01:08:42,490 --> 01:08:43,830
给我
Give it to me.

910
01:08:48,660 --> 01:08:50,210
谢谢
Thank you.

911
01:09:07,100 --> 01:09:09,770
你确信那辆汽车跟了你一天吗
You sure
that car was following you all day?

912
01:09:10,020 --> 01:09:11,860
你接上 我就开始
As soon as you picked me up. Why?

913
01:09:18,150 --> 01:09:21,950
这辆车属于乐班德尔公司
lt's registered to a company
called Lebendauer Enterprises.

914
01:09:32,540 --> 01:09:35,880
预谋杀死五个平民
A conspiracy to kill five random people?

915
01:09:37,210 --> 01:09:38,710
荒唐
That's ridiculous.

916
01:09:41,210 --> 01:09:42,560
四个
Four.

917
01:09:44,050 --> 01:09:45,890
四个平民
Four random people.

918
01:09:47,390 --> 01:09:49,520
为了掩盖一个特定的目标
To hide one specific target.

919
01:10:13,710 --> 01:10:17,210
有人想要奥赖恩-阿彻的建筑生意
Someone needed
Oline Archer's construction business.

920
01:10:19,880 --> 01:10:22,300
而奥赖恩不愿意交出项目
And Oline wouldn't let it go.

921
01:10:32,560 --> 01:10:34,810
这是一个合理的假设
lt's a convincing theory.

922
01:10:37,650 --> 01:10:39,490
但是只是一个假设
But it's just a theory.

923
01:10:40,820 --> 01:10:45,320
第一枪射击是最不准确的
The first round is the least accurate.
The snipers call it a cold shot.

924
01:10:45,570 --> 01:10:47,660
狙击手称之为冷射
你的目击证人描述说
Meanwhile, your eyewitness
described a pause

925
01:10:47,820 --> 01:10:50,080
第一枪和第二枪之间有停顿
between the first and second rounds.

926
01:10:50,660 --> 01:10:53,080
第二枪射手很深稳
The one shot where the killer
took his time.

927
01:10:53,330 --> 01:10:55,920
奥赖恩-阿彻是第二个遇害者
And Oline Archer
was the second victim.

928
01:10:56,160 --> 01:10:58,840
这一枪 至关重要
The one shot that mattered.

929
01:11:00,670 --> 01:11:02,300
这还只是猜测
But it's just a theory.

930
01:11:03,670 --> 01:11:05,420
这是根据巴尔习惯而设的圈套
This frame was custom made for Barr.

931
01:11:06,340 --> 01:11:08,220
选中他的人了解巴格达的事
Whoever chose him
knew about Baghdad

932
01:11:08,300 --> 01:11:09,970
而能讲出这件事的人
and the only one who could have
told him about Baghdad

933
01:11:10,050 --> 01:11:11,600
只有巴尔他自己
was Barr himself.

934
01:11:11,680 --> 01:11:15,180
他至少会有一朋友 非常亲密的朋友
He has at least one friend.
A very close one.

935
01:11:15,520 --> 01:11:17,860
找到他 才能找真正的凶手
Now, you find that friend,
you'll find the real shooter.

936
01:11:18,100 --> 01:11:19,600
找到真正的凶手 雷彻
Find the real shooter? Reacher,

937
01:11:19,690 --> 01:11:22,530
我的工作是向陪审团提出合理质疑
my job is to present the jury
with reasonable doubt. Period.

938
01:11:22,610 --> 01:11:24,110
-要抓那些坏人 把他们绳之以法
-让他们接受法律制裁
What about catching the guys
who really did this?

939
01:11:24,197 --> 01:11:26,282
-Catching the guys who did this?
-Bringing them to justice?

940
01:11:26,360 --> 01:11:28,520
- 不 我不能拿这到法院
- 揭开事实真相
-No, l can't take this to court.
-Exposing the truth.

941
01:11:28,530 --> 01:11:32,200
即使我相信巴尔是无辜的
Even if l believed Barr is innocent,
it's not my job.

942
01:11:33,030 --> 01:11:36,710
那不是我的工作 
我只是一个律师而不是警察
l am just a lawyer. l'm not a cop.

943
01:11:39,870 --> 01:11:41,880
而且坦白说 你也不是
And frankly, neither are you.

944
01:11:45,710 --> 01:11:47,720
我不能再这样做
l can't do this any more.

945
01:11:52,600 --> 01:11:54,440
谢谢你的咖啡 大律师
Thanks for the coffee, counsellor.

946
01:12:30,220 --> 01:12:31,390
桑迪
Sandy?

947
01:12:34,930 --> 01:12:36,400
等等 是桑迪 不是吗
Wait, it is Sandy, isn't it?

948
01:12:38,600 --> 01:12:39,650
我认识你吗
Do l know you?

949
01:12:41,440 --> 01:12:44,150
查理 杰布的朋友?
Charlie. Jeb's friend?

950
01:12:44,690 --> 01:12:46,410
太让我伤心了
Oh, come on, don't break my heart.

951
01:12:47,440 --> 01:12:49,030
对不起 我不记得
l'm sorry, l don't remember.

952
01:12:50,110 --> 01:12:51,990
我们当时都喝高了
Well, we were both pretty wasted.

953
01:12:53,660 --> 01:12:54,750
哦 对

954
01:12:55,997 --> 01:12:57,039
Yeah.

955
01:12:58,950 --> 01:13:01,800
- 什么 你住在这儿
- 就在这楼上 真巧
-What, you live here?
-Just up there.

956
01:13:02,128 --> 01:13:03,462
No shit.

957
01:13:04,000 --> 01:13:07,170
我刚刚搬到那后面住
l just moved in around the back!
How crazy is that?

958
01:13:07,800 --> 01:13:09,010
难以置信 有趣
lt's wild.

959
01:13:09,090 --> 01:13:10,140
是啊
Yeah.

960
01:13:11,470 --> 01:13:14,970
哇 你真漂亮
Wow! You look great.

961
01:13:15,800 --> 01:13:17,100
谢谢
Thanks.

962
01:13:18,140 --> 01:13:21,360
听着 我不想耽误你的时间
Well, look, you know,
l don't want to keep you, so...

963
01:13:21,430 --> 01:13:23,030
也许我们可以找个时间喝一杯
Maybe we can grab a drink sometime.

964
01:13:23,140 --> 01:13:24,570
是的  也许
Yeah, maybe.

965
01:13:25,980 --> 01:13:27,400
今晚怎么样
Hey, how about tonight?

966
01:13:28,730 --> 01:13:30,450
我约了人
l'm meeting some people.

967
01:13:31,150 --> 01:13:34,200
好吧
Okay. Well, some other time, then.

968
01:13:34,490 --> 01:13:35,830
那就改天吧
Some other time.

969
01:13:35,910 --> 01:13:37,000
在这里动手
Do it here.

970
01:13:37,120 --> 01:13:38,160
什么
What?

971
01:14:20,530 --> 01:14:21,710
雷彻
Reacher!

972
01:14:37,050 --> 01:14:40,730
俄亥俄州有个射击场
目标距离700码
There's a gun range in Ohio,
targets out to 700 yards.

973
01:14:41,220 --> 01:14:43,900
唯一符合你要求的场地
The only range
that matches your requirements.

974
01:14:48,560 --> 01:14:49,980
你应该睡一会
You should sleep.

975
01:14:51,730 --> 01:14:53,150
明天要开长途
You have a long drive tomorrow,

976
01:14:53,230 --> 01:14:55,910
我要查一下奥赖恩
and l need to go to city hall
and pull up Oline's legal history.

977
01:14:57,740 --> 01:15:00,910
先别那样做
l wouldn't do that. Not till l get back.

978
01:15:01,410 --> 01:15:04,210
等我回来再说 如果我是对的
有人杀了四个平民
lf l'm right,
someone killed four random people

979
01:15:04,290 --> 01:15:06,460
目的不是让调查员去查奥赖恩
so no one would look directly at Oline.

980
01:15:06,830 --> 01:15:10,340
如果我分析得对
只要提他的名字 你就会送命
And if l'm right, just saying her name
could get you killed.

981
01:15:10,420 --> 01:15:13,170
- 你认为我会害怕吗
- 你很聪明 那不是明摆着的吗
-You saying l should be scared?
-Well, are you smart?

982
01:15:13,670 --> 01:15:14,720
显然
Obviously.

983
01:15:14,920 --> 01:15:16,170
那就不用害怕
Then don't be scared.

984
01:15:48,960 --> 01:15:51,130
到底要我找什么
What exactly am l looking for?

985
01:15:51,630 --> 01:15:54,800
杀死这个女孩的人
Someone who could kill that girl
with one punch.

986
01:15:55,960 --> 01:15:58,310
你要的人在1109室
Oh, you want the guy in 1109.

987
01:15:59,130 --> 01:16:00,640
厄尼-约翰逊
Ernie Johnson.

988
01:16:02,220 --> 01:16:03,270
你要看看吗
You'll see.

989
01:17:28,890 --> 01:17:30,440
快下车
Out of the car!

990
01:17:37,400 --> 01:17:40,240
他是我们要抓的嫌疑犯 快跑
That's our suspect! Move, move!

991
01:18:01,760 --> 01:18:04,180
疑犯在65号公路向北行驶
Suspect is headed north
on State Route 65.

992
01:18:04,260 --> 01:18:05,850
我需要增援和空中支援
l need backup and air support.

993
01:23:38,130 --> 01:23:39,480
等一下
Hold up!

994
01:23:39,840 --> 01:23:41,190
没有人
All clear!

995
01:24:03,370 --> 01:24:06,040
哦 天呐 
我就是不敢相信 不敢相信
Oh, God,
l just don't believe it. l don't believe it!

996
01:24:06,160 --> 01:24:07,790
我刚签发了逮捕令
l issued the warrant an hour ago.

997
01:24:07,870 --> 01:24:09,290
有人看到雷彻
According to the victim's boss,

998
01:24:09,370 --> 01:24:11,050
今天去了她的商店
Reacher was seen at her
place of work this morning.

999
01:24:11,330 --> 01:24:12,800
他还威胁她老板
Where he threatened her boss.

1000
01:24:12,880 --> 01:24:15,880
他开的是杰布-奥利沃朋友的车
The car he was driving tonight
belonged to a friend of Jeb Oliver's.

1001
01:24:16,000 --> 01:24:17,130
他打了那个人
The man he assaulted.

1002
01:24:17,340 --> 01:24:18,970
不 是他们打了雷彻
No, those guys assaulted Reacher.

1003
01:24:19,050 --> 01:24:20,930
在杰布家
Reacher put three more men
in the hospital

1004
01:24:21,010 --> 01:24:22,490
雷彻把三个人打伤住院
this afternoon at Jeb Oliver's place.

1005
01:24:22,550 --> 01:24:24,730
是开杰布的车去的那里
After arriving in Jeb Oliver's car.

1006
01:24:24,850 --> 01:24:27,020
杰布出院后 再也没人看见他
And Jeb hasn't been seen
since he left the hospital.

1007
01:24:27,220 --> 01:24:29,730
如果你知道雷彻在哪  告诉我们
Helen, if you know where Reacher is,
you need to tell us.

1008
01:24:29,850 --> 01:24:31,350
我不知道 几个小时前 
我离开办公室后
l don't know where he is.
l have not seen him

1009
01:24:31,480 --> 01:24:33,900
就再也没见到他
since he left my office a few hours ago.

1010
01:24:36,020 --> 01:24:38,620
- 我认为她说是的实话
- 你认为 爸 该死
-l think she's telling the truth.
-You think, Dad? Fuck you!

1011
01:24:38,860 --> 01:24:40,830
我告诉过你不要接近他
Hey, l told you not to go near him.

1012
01:24:40,900 --> 01:24:43,330
你进入我的家就像审犯人一样审我
You come into my home
and you treat me like l'm an accessory!

1013
01:24:43,412 --> 01:24:45,497
-Please! You know...
-All right. All right. Come on. Enough.

1014
01:24:45,580 --> 01:24:46,670
- 好了 我来处理
- 我没说完
-Look, let me handle it.
-l'm not done.

1015
01:24:46,870 --> 01:24:47,990
你俩说完了 出去
You're both done. Just get out.

1016
01:24:53,540 --> 01:24:54,760
这是海伦
This is Helen.

1017
01:24:54,880 --> 01:24:56,300
我猜警察在那里
-l'm guessing the police are there?
-Yep.

1018
01:24:56,380 --> 01:24:57,430
是的

1019
01:24:57,550 --> 01:24:59,640
我猜不出30秒
By your response l'm guessing
l have about 30 seconds

1020
01:24:59,720 --> 01:25:00,960
他们就会要你手里的电话
before you hand them the phone.

1021
01:25:01,050 --> 01:25:02,390
会的
lf that.

1022
01:25:02,590 --> 01:25:04,310
如果他们能陷害巴尔
lf you believe someone
could frame Barr,

1023
01:25:04,390 --> 01:25:06,760
也能陷害我
you have to believe
they could do the same to me.

1024
01:25:06,890 --> 01:25:08,560
我想有这个可能
l suppose that's possible.

1025
01:25:09,770 --> 01:25:11,770
她是一个可爱的孩子 海伦
She was a sweet kid, Helen.

1026
01:25:12,940 --> 01:25:14,940
他们是因为我 才杀死了她
And they killed her because of me.

1027
01:25:16,270 --> 01:25:17,950
他们逼我不插手此事
They want me to run.

1028
01:25:19,030 --> 01:25:20,030
我决不
But l won't.

1029
01:25:20,610 --> 01:25:23,030
-我一定要查清
-这不是个好主意
-l'm going to finish this.
-No, that's not a good idea.

1030
01:25:23,110 --> 01:25:24,210
听好
Listen.

1031
01:25:24,410 --> 01:25:27,410
第二
Two things. One, l...

1032
01:25:28,290 --> 01:25:29,910
我偷了你的汽车
l stole your car.

1033
01:25:30,910 --> 01:25:32,590
如果你要结束合作
lf you want to end this,

1034
01:25:32,710 --> 01:25:34,050
挂上电话报案 车丢了
just hang up the phone
and report it missing.

1035
01:25:34,120 --> 01:25:35,300
我能理解
And l'll understand.

1036
01:25:35,460 --> 01:25:36,800
还有事吗
And anything else?

1037
01:25:37,460 --> 01:25:39,680
早点告诉你怕你接受不了
l thought l'd be pushing it
if l mentioned this earlier.

1038
01:25:39,760 --> 01:25:41,630
我担心发生意外
Now l guess all bets are off.

1039
01:25:42,090 --> 01:25:44,930
对爱默生和你父亲谈话要小心
You need to watch what you say
to Emerson and your father.

1040
01:25:45,140 --> 01:25:46,560
我认为他们的其中之一参与了此案
l think one of them is in on it.

1041
01:25:46,640 --> 01:25:48,980
好  谢谢通知 我挂了
All right. Thanks for calling. l have to go.

1042
01:25:49,100 --> 01:25:51,150
等等 从第一天开始 我就被跟踪了
Wait. l've been followed from day one.

1043
01:25:53,100 --> 01:25:54,770
只有三个人知道我在这里
Only three people knew l was here.

1044
01:25:54,940 --> 01:25:57,160
爱默生，你的父亲和你
Emerson, your father and you.

1045
01:25:58,150 --> 01:26:00,030
你自己想下
You need to ask yourself,

1046
01:26:00,110 --> 01:26:01,950
帮巴尔洗清罪名 谁损失最大
who has the most to lose
if we clear Barr?

1047
01:26:03,990 --> 01:26:06,330
谁警告你要离开我
Who tried to warn you off me?

1048
01:26:07,820 --> 01:26:10,330
当然 我可能是错误的
如果你认为我是
Of course, l could be wrong.
