听着 你这个混蛋
Listen to me, you prick.

1223
01:40:57,460 --> 01:40:59,460
你要是不过来 我就杀了这个婊子
l will kill this bitch
if you're not here in one...

1224
01:41:00,840 --> 01:41:02,140
该死
Shit!

1225
01:41:08,520 --> 01:41:10,140
你认为我是个英雄的
You think l'm a hero?

1226
01:41:10,350 --> 01:41:14,200
我不是英雄 我只是个游侠
l am not a hero.
l'm a drifter with nothing to lose.

1227
01:41:14,520 --> 01:41:17,370
你杀了那个女孩来陷害我
You killed that girl to put me in a frame.

1228
01:41:17,480 --> 01:41:21,490
我要扒了你的皮 喝干你的血
l mean to beat you to death
and drink your blood from a boot.

1229
01:41:22,360 --> 01:41:26,040
听着 这么办吧 你给我地址
Now, this is how it's going to work.
You're gonna give me the address

1230
01:41:26,200 --> 01:41:28,620
等我准备好了 就去找你算账
and l'll be along
when l am damn good and ready.

1231
01:41:28,700 --> 01:41:30,960
如果我打电话她不接
lf she doesn't answer the phone
when l call this number,

1232
01:41:31,040 --> 01:41:32,880
我会认为你杀了她
if l even think you've hurt her,

1233
01:41:33,210 --> 01:41:34,710
我就消失
l disappear.

1234
01:41:34,830 --> 01:41:39,640
如果你聪明点 我不是威胁你
你在明我在暗
And if you're smart, that scares you,
because l'm in your blind spot

1235
01:41:39,710 --> 01:41:41,840
而且我又没有别的事要做
and l have nothing better to do.

1236
01:41:50,060 --> 01:41:51,100
你有笔吗
You got a pen?

1237
01:41:53,230 --> 01:41:54,570
不需要
Don't need one.

1238
01:42:58,960 --> 01:43:03,470
如果每次军方来找陆战队员帮忙
我都收一美元好了
