你在开玩笑, 对不对
You're kidding, right?

1242
01:43:15,430 --> 01:43:16,900
虽然我十年前看过你射击
Just because l saw you
shoot ten years ago

1243
01:43:16,980 --> 01:43:20,450
可并不意味着我会让你用我的枪
doesn't mean l'll let you
kill some asshole with my gun.

1244
01:43:20,650 --> 01:43:22,370
我告诉过你情况非常危急
l told you how serious this was.

1245
01:43:22,650 --> 01:43:24,320
我也被卷进去了 对吗
And l showed up, didn't l?

1246
01:43:25,150 --> 01:43:26,320
咱们大干一场吧
So let's get to it.

1247
01:43:28,280 --> 01:43:29,330
杀你的凶手会到这来
Now, your shooter will be

1248
01:43:29,820 --> 01:43:32,920
在那些灯光后面
right up there
behind those lights. Okay?

1249
01:43:32,990 --> 01:43:35,960
他能朝这条路射击
He can cover both roads
coming and going.

1250
01:43:36,460 --> 01:43:39,830
你一站起来就能击毙你
And kill you
just as soon as you stand up.

1251
01:43:39,960 --> 01:43:41,130
好吧 你能干掉了吗
Well, can you take him out?

1252
01:43:41,670 --> 01:43:42,920
什么 干掉他
What, to dinner you mean?

1253
01:43:45,010 --> 01:43:49,350
听着 雷彻
我不知道你都和什么人交往
Look, l don't know the type of people
you normally associate with, Reacher.

1254
01:43:49,680 --> 01:43:54,680
我没那个习惯 毫无准备就走进荒野
But l'm not in the habit of driving out
to the boonies at the drop of a hat

1255
01:43:55,140 --> 01:43:58,490
解决掉几个陌生人 好吗
and just picking off 
some total strangers, all right?

1256
01:43:59,350 --> 01:44:02,200
那些灯太亮 我什么也看不清
Anyway, l can't see anything,
not with them lights up.

1257
01:44:02,310 --> 01:44:03,860
那就打灭它
So shoot them out.

1258
01:44:04,650 --> 01:44:07,400
可以
然后他就知道我在哪了
Yeah, sure.
And then he knows right where l am.

1259
01:44:07,490 --> 01:44:09,490
我这不是引火烧身吗
l might as well set myself on fire.

1260
01:44:10,530 --> 01:44:13,410
不 先生 他开枪 我才开枪
No, sir. l'll start shooting when he does.

1261
01:44:16,040 --> 01:44:18,160
你说我们引他先开枪怎么样
And how do you propose
we get him started?

1262
01:44:18,710 --> 01:44:22,510
好吧  你可以开始跑了
Well, you could always start running.

1263
01:44:30,010 --> 01:44:31,560
你的眼睛怎么了
What's wrong with your eye?

1264
01:44:31,680 --> 01:44:33,350
闭目养神
l'm saving my night vision.

1265
01:44:36,390 --> 01:44:40,570
